version_description: Drum-roll please: We now support Facebook Login and Sign-up!
-You spoke, we listened: GIPHY now allows sharing to WhatsApp for all your GIF needs!
You can now save a GIF as a Live Photo! Tap the Live Photo icon in the expanded sharing menu to convert any GIF in the GIPHY library, then save it as your new animated lockscreen.
WhatsApp is back + some other small bug fixes!
- Misc bug fixes
- More bug fixes and polish

Check out the new and improved UI for finding and sharing stickers and GIFs in Messages!
We also fixed an issue sharing to Facebook and Twitter from the app on iOS 11.
Logging in via your Facebook account works again too.

See anything weird? E-mail us at support@giphy.com.
Bug fixes and performance improvements

We update the app every few weeks to keep it fresh! Some things we never stop doing are code cleanup, bug fixes, and general optimization.
See anything weird? E-mail us at support@giphy.com and we'll help you out.

Fixed a bug in the Messages extension that could cause it to crash when trying to send a GIF

So much new stuff! Here's some of it:
- Upload GIFs! Take a video and convert it to a GIF, select from your camera roll, or paste a GIF link.
- MORE stickers in Messages. Browse through tons of packs or search by GIF or sticker.
- Choose from top Reaction categories in Messages to say what you mean, faster.
- Recently sent GIFs and stickers are saved for your convenience below the search bar.
- As always, more improvements under the hood.

We gave the app a facelift! Check out the new navigation, easily find GIFs and stickers on the Explore tab, and continue browsing while you upload a GIF or two.

As always, some code cleanup, bug fixes, and general optimization. Was the app crashing on you? We fixed that too.
See anything weird? E-mail us at support@giphy.com and we'll help you out.
